details.description:
InstaDeep delivers AI-powered decision-making systems for the Enterprise, to solve complex industrial problems. InstaDeep is a creator of a platform for making decisions that will guarantee talent retention and offer training.

The company's platform provides a variety of AI programs, such as enhanced pattern recognition, insights accelerated by GPUs, self-learning decision-making systems, machine learning, and predictive analytics to optimize decisions. This enables businesses to increase return on investments by enhancing manufacturing, logistics, mobility, and energy efficiency.

InstaDeep was established on October 8, 2015 by Zohra Slim and Karim Beguir in London, England.
